text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It combines
information on suffrage, the freedom and fairness of elections, freedoms of association and expression,
as well as the extent to which the protection of rights, access to power, and distribution of resources is
equal. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic).
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); Gapminder (v6); HYDE (v3.2); UN (2022)
